partnerDetails.about: Khayisa Electrical Suppliers was established in 1999 and became a member of the Independent Wholesalers Association “Electrobase (Pty) Ltd” in 2003. This association represents its members in negotiations with suppliers and ensures that as members, we are able to obtain the best possible price on products.
